Package it.polimi.travlendarplus.entities.travelMeans

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PrivateTravelMean
    This JPA class represent a private travel mean, that is any travel mean owned and used by the user ( ex. personal car or bike )
    PublicTravelMean
    This JPA class represent a public travel mean, that is any travel mean which is shared by many individuals and provided by a transport service provider (ex. bus, train , subway ...)
    SharingTravelMean
    This JPA class represent a travel mean offered in sharing
    TravelMean
    This JPA class represent a generic travel mean, is to be extended by all travel means classes
    TravelMeanTests  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TravelMeanEnum
    Enum that represent all supported travel means in Travlendar+ application
